-- NTT Communications to Offer Internet Phone for Companies, Sankei Reports
-- B y   N a o k o   F u j i m u r a
-- 2010-11-03T00:48:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-03/ntt-communications-to-offer-internet-phone-for-companies-sankei-reports.html
 NTT Communications Corp. will offer
an Internet telephone service that allows corporate customers to
communicate between their Japan and overseas offices from
December, the Sankei newspaper reported, without saying where it
got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
